    <note type="biography">
        <p>Botanist. Assistant in the botanical department of the British Museum, 1869–79. Appointed to succeed George Henry Kendrick Thwaites as director of the Peradeniya botanic gardens, Ceylon (Sri Lanka), in 1879. Editor of the <hi rend="italic">Journal of Botany</hi>, 1871–96. Brother of Roland Trimen. FRS 1888.</p></note>
